projDesc: This React App is inspired by Google Keep that allows users to create, edit, and delete notes and also utilizes local storage to save user data.
This static page is built using html and css
Full Authentication Project including basic Login to Encryption and Authentication using EJS, Mongoose, Passport, mongoDB, and others.
This React app with a simple and intuitive interface helps you add and delete tasks as you complete them.
It includes note creation, editing, and deletion, with markdown syntax for formatting and image/link insertion and also localStorage for offline note saving.
